# ========================================
# Notes
# ========================================
# This .gitignore prioritizes privacy and confidentiality
# Original student documents MUST NEVER be committed
# Only anonymized, sanitized examples should be in the repository
#
# Before committing ANY audit report, ensure:
# 1. Student names are removed or anonymized
# 2. Institution identifiers are removed
# 3. Supervisor names are removed
# 4. Document titles are generalized
# 5. Sensitive content is redacted
#
# Use: git status --ignored
# To verify what's being excluded
